experiences.jobDescription:
oneUp delivers startup thinking for corporates, and in this case oneUp was building a loyalty program called MYTOMMY; an app that's part of the Tommy Hilfiger ecosystem. As growth marketer it was my duty to further strengthen the efforts of making the app successful.

I've supported the project with:
* Interviewing stakeholders and creating a measurement framework in which success was defined;
* Getting performance information to the right people at the right time;
* Being the MixPanel GoTo guy if app user data was needed;
* Analysing experiments, documenting learnings, and creating hypothesis for new experiments;
* Running experiments;
* Building the bridge between the MYTOMMY data and the CRM data of PVH.

- Google Analytics;
- Google Adwords;
- On- and off-site SEO.
